%% Diagram: IndexedDB version upgrade handshake across tabs
%% Type: sequenceDiagram
sequenceDiagram
    participant TabA as Tab A (v2 open)
    participant DB as IndexedDB
    participant TabB as Tab B (opening v3)

    TabB->>DB: indexedDB.open("myapp", 3)
    DB-->>TabA: versionchange event
    Note over TabA: Must call db.close()<br/>to release the connection
    TabA->>DB: db.close()
    DB->>TabB: upgradeneeded (oldVersion=2)
    Note over TabB: Schema migrations run<br/>inside versionchange tx
    TabB->>DB: createObjectStore / createIndex
    DB-->>TabB: success
    Note over DB: If TabA never closes,<br/>TabB gets a blocked event<br/>and the upgrade waits.
